The Romans Recycle: Wickenby, Lincolnshire.
Tony Robinson and his intrepid team of archaeologists head off the beaten track in Lincolnshire to discover why a metal

detector enthusiast has discovered hundreds of Roman and Iron Age finds in a muddy field. Add to that the mysterious Roman
